<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>택스 파트너 - 절세의 정석</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            calc: '#2C3E50',
            paper: '#ECF0F1',
            pen: '#E74C3C',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            mono: ['Roboto Mono', 'monospace'],
            sans: ['Noto Sans KR', 'sans-serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-paper text-calc font-sans border-t-8 border-calc">

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="container mx-auto px-8 py-6 flex justify-between items-center">
    <div class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="text-pen text-3xl">TAX</span> PARTNER
    </div>
    <div class="hidden md:flex gap-10 font-mono text-sm font-bold text-gray-500">
      <a href="#service" class="hover:text-calc transition">SERVICES</a>
      <a href="#calculator" class="hover:text-calc transition">CALCULATOR</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-calc transition">CONTACT</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="py-24 px-8 container mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <div class="space-y-8 animate-fade-in">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Save More, <br>
        <span class="text-pen">Worry Less.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
        복잡한 세금, 전문가에게 맡기세요. <br>
        합법적인 절세 전략으로 당신의 소중한 자산을 지켜드립니다.
      </p>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border-l-4 border-pen shadow-lg max-w-md">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">무료 세금 진단</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">간단한 정보 입력으로 예상 환급액을 확인해보세요.</p>
        <button onclick="toggleTax()" class="bg-calc text-white w-full py-4 font-bold hover:bg-black transition">
          진단 시작하기 &rarr;
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Calculator Graphic -->
    <div class="relative bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-200 transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition duration-500">
      <div class="font-mono text-right text-4xl text-gray-400 mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded">
        ₩ 15,240,000
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 font-mono font-bold text-xl text-gray-600">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-200">AC</div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-200">+/-</div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-200">%</div>
        <div class="bg-pen text-white p-4 rounded text-center">÷</div>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">7</div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">8</div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">9</div>
        <div class="bg-calc text-white p-4 rounded text-center">×</div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">4</div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">5</div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">6</div>
        <div class="bg-calc text-white p-4 rounded text-center">-</div>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">1</div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">2</div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">3</div>
        <div class="bg-calc text-white p-4 rounded text-center">+</div>
        
        <div class="col-span-2 bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">0</div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-gray-50">.</div>
        <div class="bg-pen text-white p-4 rounded text-center">=</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Services List -->
  <section id="service" class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 relative inline-block">
            Our Solutions
            <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-1/3 h-1 bg-pen"></div>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-loose">
            개인 사업자부터 법인까지, <br>
            각 단계에 맞는 최적의 세무 솔루션을 제공합니다. <br>
            기장 대리, 신고 대행, 세무 조사 대응 등 <br>
            모든 세무 업무를 원스톱으로 처리해 드립니다.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Item -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 border border-gray-100 hover:border-calc transition cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleTax()">
            <div class="bg-paper p-3 rounded text-2xl">📋</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">기장 대리</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">체계적인 장부 관리로 절세의 기초를 다집니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Item -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 border border-gray-100 hover:border-calc transition cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleTax()">
            <div class="bg-paper p-3 rounded text-2xl">💰</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">양도 / 상속 / 증여</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">자산 이전 시 발생하는 세금을 최소화합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Item -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 border border-gray-100 hover:border-calc transition cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleTax()">
            <div class="bg-paper p-3 rounded text-2xl">🏢</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">법인 설립 / 전환</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">사업 확장을 위한 최적의 구조를 설계합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modal -->
  <div id="tax-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-calc/90 z-[60] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-white w-full max-w-md p-8 relative shadow-2xl border-t-8 border-pen">
      <button onclick="toggleTax()" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-400 hover:text-calc text-2xl">&times;</button>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">무료 상담 신청</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">복잡한 세금 고민, 지금 바로 해결하세요.</p>
      </div>

      <form class="space-y-4" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('상담 신청이 완료되었습니다.'); toggleTax();">
        <input type="text" placeholder="사업장명 / 성함" class="w-full bg-paper p-4 font-bold outline-none border-2 border-transparent focus:border-calc">
        <input type="tel" placeholder="연락처" class="w-full bg-paper p-4 font-bold outline-none border-2 border-transparent focus:border-calc">
        <select class="w-full bg-paper p-4 font-bold outline-none border-2 border-transparent focus:border-calc text-gray-600">
           <option>관심 분야 선택</option>
           <option>기장 대리 문의</option>
           <option>양도세 상담</option>
           <option>상속/증여세 상담</option>
           <option>법인 설립/전환</option>
        </select>
        
        <button class="w-full bg-pen text-white py-4 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-red-600 transition shadow-lg mt-2">
          상담 신청하기
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function toggleTax() {
      const modal = document.getElementById('tax-modal');
      if(modal.classList.contains('hidden')) {
        modal.classList.remove('hidden');
      } else {
        modal.classList.add('hidden');
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
